    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/608d3fa6f9c3dd49e1fc7a1af772b2b3.poster.avif?t=1707412819\" width=616 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/608d3fa6f9c3dd49e1fc7a1af772b2b3.webm?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/608d3fa6f9c3dd49e1fc7a1af772b2b3.mp4?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>WORLDSLAYER扩展包将允许《Outriders》的拥有者直接体验全新的WORLDSLAYER游戏内容。<br><br>挑战全新的恐怖，探索前所未有的武器、模块与装备，通过全新的帕克斯混合分支职业专长树进一步打造属于你的角色配置。<br><br>完成战役并见证全新的终局内容，在塔亚格拉塔的试炼中面对难以想象的恐怖。除此以外，巅峰点数还将为最为努力的玩家们提供全新的长期升级体系。<br><br>最后，勇敢挑战全新的末世难度等级并逐步提升至40级，你将会有更高的机会获取无与伦比的末世装备并享受到足以改变一切的第三个模块。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/c4fbfaefcc1beed9360224d64eb0928e.webp?t=1707412819\" width=618 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/afee7e84eb85410c3021c943eb0a0b5b.poster.avif?t=1707412819\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/afee7e84eb85410c3021c943eb0a0b5b.webm?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/afee7e84eb85410c3021c943eb0a0b5b.mp4?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>帕克斯树<br>帕克斯树正式登场。为每个职业技能树添加2个分支，带来更丰富的自定义选项来助你深入专精某一职业或打造全新混合职业。<br><br>巅峰点数<br>巅峰点数是专为强化玩家所设计的长期进度系统。击杀敌人、获得经验就能提升等级，从四种巅峰类别来进一步强化你的Outrider。从残暴、耐久、英勇和异能方面来自定义你的Outrider。末世等级<br>新的末世等级系统除了能够提升玩家的最大装备等级还有增加难度外，更重要的是还能提高战役模式和游戏终局阶段的战利品等级。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/c4fbfaefcc1beed9360224d64eb0928e.webp?t=1707412819\" width=618 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/1bdcdbd002eb0db514d0ab600529a557.poster.avif?t=1707412819\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/1bdcdbd002eb0db514d0ab600529a557.webm?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/1bdcdbd002eb0db514d0ab600529a557.mp4?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>末世等级战利品<br>新的末世武器和护甲让你比以往更加强大。新增职业限定的传奇护甲套装与全职业共通的3件组套装。且全都有套装加成。第3个模块栏位<br>所有新的末世装备都新增了致命的第3个模块字段，提高玩家的杀戮之力跟装备选择的自由度。<br><br>新模块<br>添加了新模块，强势增强你的生存力与伤害能力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/c4fbfaefcc1beed9360224d64eb0928e.webp?t=1707412819\" width=618 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/0ee44ad105dbdfcc7d5c8b9adcf977aa.poster.avif?t=1707412819\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/0ee44ad105dbdfcc7d5c8b9adcf977aa.webm?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/0ee44ad105dbdfcc7d5c8b9adcf977aa.mp4?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>直面死亡<br>作为人类生存的最后希望，深入伊诺克星文明的摇篮。<br><br>动态化的1-3名玩家合作游玩<br>单打独斗或者是在随时加入随时离开的合作模式中与至多2位好友共同面对末日星球上超进化后的恐怖生物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/c4fbfaefcc1beed9360224d64eb0928e.webp?t=1707412819\" width=618 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/60f0bb029587e2a03ae3c1869dda0115.poster.avif?t=1707412819\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/60f0bb029587e2a03ae3c1869dda0115.webm?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/60f0bb029587e2a03ae3c1869dda0115.mp4?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>4种独特职业<br>进一步培养现有角色，或者直接创造并定制全新的Outrider。4种独特的强大职业各自拥有着不同的爽快能力，使用技能树与帕克斯树进一步打造独一无二的游玩风格。<br><br>枪械&amp;装备<br>使用全新的强大末世物品与模块改造并升级你的Outrider。末世物品以及其拥有的第三个模块将允许你随心所欲打造出属于自己游戏风格的配置。而且所有物品都能享用到完整的免费幻化系统。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/c4fbfaefcc1beed9360224d64eb0928e.webp?t=1707412819\" width=618 height=34 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/308737fb8bd8982e43d7c511ccddef06.poster.avif?t=1707412819\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/308737fb8bd8982e43d7c511ccddef06.webm?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785250/extras/308737fb8bd8982e43d7c511ccddef06.mp4?t=1707412819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>力量<br>通过庞大的职业技能树以及帕克斯树调整你的能力与技能，享受混合分支加成。挑战末世等级，宣泄无与伦比的力量并使用巅峰点数提升残暴、耐久、英勇与异能。<br><br>终局<br>获取难以想象的战利品，在远古都市塔亚格拉塔的终局体验中对抗全新的恐怖存在。<br><br>一步到位<br>进一步培养自己现有的角色，或者使用全新快速提升机制获取一个装备齐全的30级Outrider并立即见证刺激惊险的战斗。",
